description:
The What-If Tool makes it easy to efficiently and intuitively explore up
to two models' performance on a dataset. Investigate model performances
for a range of features in your dataset, optimization strategies and
even manipulations to individual datapoint values. All this and more, in
a visual way that requires minimal code.
